evidence.text: As discussed at the hearing, the TRO granted on June 4, 2025 is hereby extended until and including June 25, 2025. In addition, the Parties are hereby ORDERED to meet and confer and file a joint status report by June 20, 2025 addressing the redactions made to the exhibits filed in support of Defendants opposition brief (Dkt. 29). (HEREBY ORDERED by Judge Andrew L. Carter, Jr) (Text Only Order) (Carter, Andrew) (Entered: 06/17/2025)
